Photo, Mohamed Abdu (far right), under Gary Stevens, holds off Peace and Alex 
Solis to win the Inglewood Handicap on the turf course at Hollywood Park 
Sunday. STEPHEN M. TOWNSLEY / Los Angeles Times 
